*libvisual-0.4.0-r1 (04 Oct 2007)

  04 Oct 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> +libvisual-0.4.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add USE flags nls, threads and debug wrt #194566 and matching deps for them.
  Use emake instead of make in src_install.

  07 Feb 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Remove static useflag, thanks to Jakub Moc in bug #165766.

  10 Dec 2006; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  force MMX on x86, to fix bug #146335

  31 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  20 Oct 2006; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  18 Oct 2006; Joshua Jackson <tsunam@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Stable x86; for amarok

  14 Oct 2006; <nixnut@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc wrt bug 150988

  14 Oct 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64; bug #150988

  14 Oct 2006; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Stable on SPARC wrt bug #150988.

*libvisual-0.4.0 (28 May 2006)

  28 May 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -files/libvisual-0.1.6-destdir.patch, -files/libvisual-0.1.6-libdir.patch,
  -libvisual-0.1.6.ebuild, -libvisual-0.1.7.ebuild, +libvisual-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Version bump to latest version upstream, slotted as this is incompatible
  with 0.2 series. Thanks to Alejandro Nova and Gleb Litvjak in bug #131733.

  24 Feb 2006; Stephen P. Becker <spbecker@gentoo.org>
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  added ~mips keyword

  11 Feb 2006; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  23 Dec 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64

  05 Jul 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  17 Jun 2005; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Marked ppc stable.

  21 May 2005; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  stable on x86 and amd64

  12 May 2005; Eldad Zack <eldad@gentoo.org>
  +files/libvisual-0.2.0-movd.patch, libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  Fixed assembler movd misuse. Patch provided by Nickolay Kolchin-Semyonov
  <nbkolchin@yandex.ru>. Closes Bug 86859.

  15 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> libvisual-0.1.6.ebuild:
  dont make use of the pic useflag any longer

  06 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> +files/0.2.0-ppc.patch,
  libvisual-0.2.0.ebuild:
  added patch to fix compilation on ppc, fixes bug #86533

